attackcastle (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package for beta distribution.
  * Add dependency bootstrap commands for apt-based tool installation.
  * Ship GUI runtime dependencies in the main package so `attackcastle gui`
    works after install.
  * Add a desktop launcher for Kali/Debian environments.

